-NHL seasons]]\n*[[List of Stanley Cup champions]]\n*[[1913\u201314 PCHA season]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n* {{cite book |\nlast=Coleman\n|first=Charles\n|title=The Trail of the Stanley Cup, Vol. 1, 1893\u20131926 inc.\n|year=1966\n|publisher=NHL\n}}\n* Podnieks, Andrew; Hockey Hall of Fame (2004). Lord Stanley's Cup. Triumph Books, 12, 50. {{ISBN|1-55168-261-3}}.\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{succession box |\n  before = [[1912\u201313 NHA season#Quebec Bulldogs 1913 Stanley Cup Champions|Quebec Bulldogs<br>1913]] |\n  after = [[1915 Stanley Cup Finals#Vancouver Millionaires 1915 Stanley Cup champions|Vancouver Millionaires<br>1915]] |\n  title = [[List of Stanley Cup champions|Toronto Hockey Club<br>Stanley Cup Champions]] |\n  years = 1914|\n}}\n{{s-end}}\n\n{{NHA seasons}}\n{{1913\u201314 NHA season by team}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:1913-14 Nha Season}}\n[[Category:1913\u201314 in Canadian ice hockey by league|NHA]]\n[[Category:National Hockey Association seasons]]\n", "name_user": "Eschoryii", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eToronto Hockey Club 1914 Stanley Cup Champions", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/1913%E2%80%9314_NHA_season"}
